Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Maison.de.章樫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗称 妖馆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖馆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不必担心 凛凛蝶小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我定会好好保护您
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了 凛凛蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也允许我接您放学 我深感荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么稍后请去用餐...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要向御狐神君表达我的谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超市抽奖中的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哐当一声 中大奖了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千野太可爱了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一身女仆装加上一脸得意的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放哪装饰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也帮你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千野 朝我这里看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不放在休息厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都往这里走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千野 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨磨蹭蹭了 渣滓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得你待人差距太大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么也请雪小路小姐多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家应该都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛凛蝶他们也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究 究竟什么状况了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妖馆的安全系统启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全系统？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人想要入侵妖馆时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全系统就会启动 形成结界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来竟然藏在盆栽里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是假死状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假死状态？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假死状态就是说之前一直在沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不被人发现 进到了里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点云里雾里的 难道是我的错？抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是小千野的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了这里还有几个结界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个结界都有一扇门和一个安全据点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个浮在那边 就说明它在正常运作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使不做那些事 只要门是紧闭着的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪就进不来 放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一打开了门怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只开了一扇门 结界都会被削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到早上 妖怪就会消失 安全系统也会解除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之前我们就在这里呆着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明天早上之前就是食人节
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生存游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此情况下 明早之前都要听我的话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是和兔子先生的约定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全剧终
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你怎么变成豆狸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过太突然吓了一跳 才变身了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这些 歌留多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里 当然是别的结界里咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能违背同兔子先生的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 是很危险的妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用语言来描述都非常可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不管怎样看来今晚就只能在这过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太悠闲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您晚饭还没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来 这些东西哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前准备好放在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来长夜漫漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野蔷薇 那边有很多东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今晚还有很多时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要守在歌留多身边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么守
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在别的结界吧 我到那个结界去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管这结界会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了救歌留多 我要撬开这扇命运之门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门到底在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了 兔子是不会说谎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在这里 你也可以为小歌歌做点什么的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这结界里面形成了无限回路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其时间流动和外面的世界是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的一小时相当于外面的一天到两天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某些地方 还很适合训练的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说这个走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板是扭曲的 在这里培养平衡感是非常有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持训练到早上的话 保证能提升你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“再也不让你们说我是病弱男孩 let's training！” 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为了小歌歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都很冷静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看上去是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你现在和平常没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到在这房间里 能服侍凛凛蝶小姐到早上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就冷静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 冷静下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门窗都不能开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在密闭的房间 到早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说青春期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 是个表达谢意的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 原来如此 哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐看来心情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.27,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:13.21,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的母亲 地球这一行星从诞生以来 过了46亿年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 猫月先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:17.53,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类作为盟主 统领着这个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会和你们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈真好呢 一家团圆的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:24.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在统领的过程中 会发生一些奇妙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我以为和团圆一词都无缘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也坐下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:29.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇妙之事一直持续发生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话题变得有点沉重呢 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 算了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我扯上关系的话 可会引火上身的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:33.62,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类始终贯彻自己的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其他物种寻求共存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 他一直都这样子 爸爸也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野蔷薇 别 突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了是第一次 要温柔点的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也来 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么进攻 我可是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千野 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然进攻这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了 我是冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下个玩花牌吧 花牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐来教你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么表达谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 果然这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 怎么能打退堂鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐 您要不要去沐浴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡？这种时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到明天早上都不能离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这么做可以放松下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 有点道理 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御狐神君 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那个... 真是麻烦你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是应尽之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 本来我也应同您一起入浴 为您擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但男女有别 不能照顾周到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗好澡之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这种东西哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到凛凛蝶小姐这种装扮 如同进入梦境般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种话就别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常可爱 多想将这样子保存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 要不要拍张照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能把它当做待机画面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把它放大 挂在墙上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也去洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事是不被允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是一条狗 却用凛凛蝶小姐用过的浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还用同一浴缸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 你别洗了就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做好您就寝的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 还不困
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御狐神君 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:13:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 明天之前我会好好保护凛凛蝶小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要不要躺下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 也能放松下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对 我就躺下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事的话 请随时吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 你别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:15:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我了 想睡的话就睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐也请别在意我 早点休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让...让...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你受累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明...明...明...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天还要上学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这番话 我受之有愧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的吧 我是为了凛凛蝶小姐而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能保护好凛凛蝶小姐的话 我的存在就毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…是凛凛蝶小姐的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对这样的我 说出这番话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,272)}{\fad(550,150)}但\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,430)}{\fad(550,150)}正\N因\N为\N如\N此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,163)}{\fad(550,850)}我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,434)}{\fad(550,850)}也\N想\N回\N报\N他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快天亮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感觉很有效果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然结界中就是不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 不会吧 你当真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不这么说 渡狸肯定会担心小歌歌的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 这个是门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 原来在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎哪扇门被打开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 别来打扰我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 渡狸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不良少年哦 尽管来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡狸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西很弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小双双 小蝶蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小双双 我还以为我们再也见不到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事真是太好了 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目先生把我们带过来的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪某个笨蛋 毁了结界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想想制伏妖怪要来的快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制伏？不危险吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没你想的那么危险 怎么说呢 就是有点麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 御狐神君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前确实说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Obariyon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别名 背负小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏于夜路 会依附到路人身上的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传言只是依附着路人 并不会加害于人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不给我放开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛凛蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我跟在您身旁 却有如此失态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些 你不是说这是非常可怕的妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那种东西碰到凛凛蝶小姐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到这我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈还蛮有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳依旧会升起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 食人节活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次教你禁忌游戏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用给她看你修行成果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃早饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛凛蝶小姐 回房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.99,0:23:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小人村千野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖馆的女仆 超喜欢打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 不是自我介绍 是要做下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.27,0:23:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.98,0:24:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回可是出浴后闷闷不乐的小凛凛蝶邀请御狐神先生的故事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得有点不对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 妖狐x仆SS 茶与距离
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.47,0:24:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完了 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥一脸得意
